title: rymdkapsel [Wineskin]
description:
Name: rymdkapsel
Year: 2014
Genre: Indie, Strategy
Kind: Wineskin
Developer: grapefrukt games
Rating: 7.5 on IGN

==============================================================

rymdkapsel is a meditative strategy game set in space. Take on the challenge of building the best possible station by commanding your minions and exploring the galaxy around you.

==============================================================

Instructions: Unzip and Play

OS: Tested and working on Mavericks and Yosemite.
